example (linsys, continued)

examine the output of the script below
play with different \(p\) values!

clc;
p=1;
nrm=@(x)norm(x,p);
cnd=@(x)cond(x,p);
A=[1,1;1,1.0001];
b0=[2;2];
b1=[2;2.0001];
x0=A\b0;
x1=A\b1;
xrel=nrm(x0-x1)/nrm(x0);
brel=nrm(b0-b1)/nrm(b0);
disp("observed: "+string(xrel/brel));
disp("theory  : "+string(cnd(A)));
